<?xml version="1.0" encoding="UTF-8"?><song><title>hǎo mù rén 迦南735</title>
<lyrics>[V1]
 wǒ men shì cǎo chǎng shàng de yáng qún, yé hé huá shì wǒ men de hǎo mù rén.
 qīng cǎo de xī shuǐ biān, ràng wǒ men ān shēn. yǒng yǒng yuǎn yuǎn bù lí kāi wǒ men.
 hǎo mù rén hǎo mù rén hǎo mù rén, wèi yáng shě mìng bǎo hù yáng qún.
 dà fēng dà làng zhōng, nǐ shì bì nán suǒ, mí shī de yáng dào chù qù zhǎo xún.
 hǎo mù rén hǎo mù rén, shí shí qiān guà yáng qún.</lyrics>
<author>lǚ xiǎo mǐn</author>
<hymn_number>735</hymn_number>
</song>